snippet.title: Kreed PC game Trailer
snippet.description:
A 2001 trailer showcasing Kreed graphic capabilities.
Kreed is a sci-fi shooter in which the player has the role of a genetically enhanced soldier on a spaceship that gets sucked into a black hole.

Kreed was released in 2003, but wasnt very popular in Europe.There is also an expansion called Battle for Savitar, but from my knowledge i heard it was only released in Russia.

Published by Russobit-M and Developed by Burut Software
